text: Trapiche de Abra () is a town in the municipality of San Martín de Hidalgo in the state of Jalisco, Mexico. It has a population of 1,115 inhabitants, 522 men, 592 women.\- Trapiche del Abra, San Martín Hidalgo, Jalisco ==References== ==External links== *Trapiche del Abra at PueblosAmerica.com Category:Populated places in Jalisco
